<h1 align="center">Why are Words Important? </h1>

<p align="left">There are many different ways to communicate, which include being verbal or non-verbal. The way we learn to communicate is very important for learning how to communicate with others in a healthy manner. Being able to express yourself is important, however not everyone learns how to do this. The resources below are there to help you learn more about how words have an effect in our lives, as well as resources on how to learn to express yourself through positive verbal communication with yourself and others.</p>

<p align="left">Learning how to be kind to yourself through the use of words is a very important part of demonstrating self-love and appreciation towards yourself. Everyone talks about making the world a better place, however, It all starts with one person. Yourself. I hope that by learning how to be kind and compassionate to yourself, youâ€™ll learn to be kind and compassionate towards others all while in the process improving your mental health.</p>

